{%- comment -%}
  Renders the gated CTA shown where price + buy-buttons would normally appear
  for non-approved viewers. Consumers check `customer.tags contains 'approved'`
  and render this snippet for the gated branch.

  Accepts:
    product       - {Product} current product context (optional)
    block_class   - {String}  optional extra class for the wrapper
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="gated-cta {{ block_class }}">
  <a href="/pages/practitioner-application" class="gated-cta__button">
    Apply for access
  </a>
  <p class="gated-cta__hint">Pricing and ordering available to verified practitioners.</p>
</div>
